GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 1007
Short Title: Human Trafficking Omnibus. (Public)
Sponsors: Senators Alexander, Barnes, and Lazzara (Primary Sponsors).
